ca.uqac.lif.labpal.table.rendering

Class TableNodeRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uqac.lif.labpal.table.rendering.TableNodeRenderer
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HtmlTableNodeRenderer, LatexTableRenderer

    public abstract class TableNodeRenderer
extends Object
    Renders a result tree as a string of a given format. Different subclasses of this class will render the tree differently.
